1
00:01:03,790 --> 00:01:05,810
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,250 --> 00:01:09,830
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:24,400
I'm the Flower Deity
in Nan'an Mansion's Rear Garden.

4
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,590
My name is Li,

5
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:29,590
a woman unwilling to be controlled

6
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:31,590
by outdated, rigid societal rules.

7
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:33,280
And he,

8
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:34,680
Zhao,

9
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,400
is my lover.

10
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:41,150
He is also my confidant.

11
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:49,680
We never ask about each other's origins.

12
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,979
We only speak of love and passion,

13
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:56,350
hoping to create our own paradise
away from the outside world

14
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:59,009
in this corner of Wenxiang Pavilion.

15
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:04,040
But tonight...

16
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,400
will be the last time...

17
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,430
we ever meet in this lifetime.

18
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,520
Everyone, listen to me.

19
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,960
To be honest,

20
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:30,680
the real good show is actually upstairs!

21
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:37,020
A high official's legitimate daughter
secretly meets her scholar lover

22
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:38,840
for an intimate rendezvous.

23
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,560
It would be a pity to miss it.

24
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,960
Don't you all want to go upstairs
and watch this good show?

25
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,030
-Yes!
-Yes!

26
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,590
Let's go!

27
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:46,720
Follow me upstairs!

28
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,470
Okay.

29
00:03:03,550 --> 00:03:05,020
-Li.
-Don't speak.

30
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,750
Zhao,

31
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,910
you are so handsome.

32
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,630
What a pity.

33
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:13,280
I'll never see you again.

34
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,680
Li,

35
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,840
what are you talking about?

36
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,770
I am already betrothed to someone.

37
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,120
We were nothing but a brief affair.

38
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,590
I'm tired of this game.

39
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,079
Let's part ways here.

40
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:25,960
You...

41
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,870
I hope
whenever you think of me in the future,

42
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:32,870
you won't forget tonight.

43
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:35,430
Li.

44
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,840
Li!

45
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:45,079
Li! Li!

46
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,910
Li!

47
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,050
Which young master is this?

48
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,560
Playing quite wildly.

49
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:15,950
[Wenxiang Pavilion]

50
00:04:29,970 --> 00:04:30,510
[Grand Tutor's legitimate daughter,
Jiang Li]

51
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,310
My Lady,

52
00:04:31,330 --> 00:04:32,730
is it really proper to be so ruthless?

53
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:33,960
[Xi'er, a maid from Jiang's Mansion]

54
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,190
Ruthless?

55
00:04:39,530 --> 00:04:41,100
[Wenxiang Pavilion]

56
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:41,890
[A few days ago]

57
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:44,000
Zhao said
he's never been to a lantern festival.

58
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,530
I'll give him this lantern
as a birthday gift.

59
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,310
I have admired you for a long time,

60
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:51,800
but everyone in Wenxiang Pavilion knows

61
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,850
you already have someone you love.

62
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,800
There are so many beauties in the world.

63
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,360
I'm just playing with her.

64
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,510
It's nothing but a brief affair.

65
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:05,390
Then I'll believe your words for now.

66
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,380
I'm tired of the shows
at Wenxiang Pavilion.

67
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:13,700
Xi'er.

68
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,660
Have you found the storytellers?

69
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:16,950
As you instructed, My Lady,

70
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:19,070
they are all top-rated storytellers
in the city.

71
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:21,830
I have plenty of romantic affairs
at Wenxiang Pavilion.

72
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,310
Have them exaggerate and embellish them,

73
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,480
and spread the stories far and wide.

74
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:27,480
Since Father is trying every way
to marry me off,

75
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,430
I can't just sit and wait for my fate.

76
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:31,720
My Lady, is this really a good idea?

77
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:34,270
This time, it was the empress dowager
who issued the decree for the marriage.

78
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,310
So what?

79
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,680
I decide my own marriage.

80
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:40,870
Once the stories
about my romantic affairs spread,

81
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:42,600
they'll back off.

82
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,190
Yes.

83
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:51,560
Zhao, since you betrayed me first,

84
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:54,159
we'll be strangers from now on.

85
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,870
May we each find our own happiness,

86
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:00,160
and never meet again.

87
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:01,950
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

88
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:05,560
This unfilial child. The empress dowager
personally bestowed the marriage.

89
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,920
If she runs away,
how am I supposed to explain?

90
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,600
Master, don't be angry.

91
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,360
[Grand Tutor of Zhao State,
Jiang Chengzhou]

92
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,920
Look, Li has returned.

93
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,970
Father, I pay my respects.

94
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:18,920
Stop!

95
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,920
You unfilial child.

96
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,750
You go out carousing every night.

97
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,830
Do you want to anger me to death?

98
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:29,120
Father, you worry too much.

99
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,400
You managed to take another wife.

100
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,750
[Grand Tutor Jiang's second wife,
Ms. Song]

101
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,480
I think you're still in good health.

102
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,270
Enough!

103
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,630
You're just as improper as your mother!

104
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,480
Once you marry into General's Mansion,

105
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:42,610
General Xun's family rules
will teach you a good lesson!

106
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,430
I'll say it again.

107
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,860
No matter who bestowed the marriage,

108
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,560
I will not marry!

109
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,120
Xi'er, let's go.

110
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:52,830
Don't you want Chunliu Garden anymore?

111
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:55,310
I knew long ago you wouldn't obey.

112
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,510
Good thing Ms. Song came up with an idea.

113
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,190
All those assets your mother left,

114
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,480
including Chunliu Garden
you've been yearning for,

115
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,190
have all been listed
on the dowry inventory

116
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:04,560
and sent to General's Mansion!

117
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,510
If you obediently marry
into General's Mansion,

118
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:10,800
we might still
maintain our father-daughter relationship!

119
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,000
If my mother

120
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:14,430
hadn't exhausted herself
to support your studies

121
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:15,960
so you could pass the exams,

122
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:16,870
Father,

123
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:19,240
you would've been nothing
but a poor scholar

124
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,000
selling calligraphy on the streets.

125
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,870
But after you passed the exams
and secured your position as Grand Tutor,

126
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:26,560
you divorced my mother
and married a noble woman.

127
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,600
And now,

128
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,680
you even want to sell your own daughter.

129
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,190
How disrespectful!

130
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,159
Punish her according to the family rules!

131
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,560
I'd like to see who dares!

132
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,800
Tomorrow, I will go to General's Mansion.

133
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,240
Chunliu Garden—

134
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,510
I'll get it back myself!

135
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,720
I'm tired of this game.

136
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:07,480
I hope
whenever you think of me in the future,

137
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:10,310
you won't forget tonight.

138
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,040
Li!

139
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:12,870
Li!

140
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:30,360
[Zhao State's emperor, Xie Jiuzhao]

141
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,840
-We pay our respects, Your Majesty!
-We pay our respects, Your Majesty!

142
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:41,510
-Long live the emperor!
-Long live the emperor!

143
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:44,960
Li, you told me not to forget tonight.

144
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,840
Even without you saying that,

145
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:49,080
I won't let this go easily.

146
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,360
You hid very well.

147
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,720
If that singer hadn't confessed,

148
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:04,480
I wouldn't have known
it was you who dared harm me.

149
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:06,080
Your Majesty, please investigate clearly!

150
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:09,000
I'm absolutely loyal to you!

151
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,080
Your Majesty,

152
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:13,370
everything has been investigated clearly.

153
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:14,870
[Commander of Imperial Guards,
Yuwen Qiang]

154
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:18,200
He was sent by the chief eunuch
serving the empress dowager.

155
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,550
And...

156
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:20,630
Go ahead.

157
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,390
Regarding Miss Jiang,

158
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:26,270
her marriage was also arranged
by the empress dowager yesterday.

159
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:29,720
The intended groom
is the current Left General,

160
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,320
Xun Simo.

161
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,720
[General's Mansion]

162
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,630
How dare you!
We don't know any Jiang family!

163
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,320
Get out!

164
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:40,840
General Xun!

165
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,150
Out!

166
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,550
If you're a man, don't be a coward!

167
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,480
Come out and see me!

168
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,200
Seize her!

169
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,120
General.

170
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,720
General.

171
00:10:06,410 --> 00:10:11,110
[Left General of Zhao State, Xun Simo]

172
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,960
She is the Jiang family's eldest daughter,

173
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,270
who is betrothed to me.

174
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,870
She's my future wife.

175
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:21,370
She's not someone
your dirty hands can touch!

176
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:22,870
Leave now!

177
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,000
-Yes!
-Yes!

178
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,120
Miss Jiang,

179
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,000
please come inside.

180
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:45,960
Miss Jiang,

181
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,480
the empress dowager
just bestowed our marriage.

182
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,440
And you're already here to see me today.

183
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,720
-Could it be...
-General Xun.

184
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,550
I'll be straightforward.

185
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,920
-About the marriage, I...
-Miss Jiang.

186
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:00,960
I can't be more pleased with our marriage,

187
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:04,320
so I absolutely will not join you

188
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,920
in rejecting this marriage.

189
00:11:07,390 --> 00:11:09,270
Let's be frank with each other.

190
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:12,030
This marriage will happen, no matter what.

191
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,670
If you have any conditions,

192
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:14,800
feel free to tell me.

193
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:18,280
He actually wants
to negotiate terms with me?

194
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,240
Since that's the case...

195
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,320
Fine.

196
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,200
General Xun, since you're so forthright,

197
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,000
I'll be straightforward too.

198
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:28,720
Originally,
I disliked this marriage arrangement.

199
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,390
But seeing how reasonable you are today

200
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,150
has somewhat changed my view.

201
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,870
My condition is very simple.

202
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,870
I hope that after the marriage,

203
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:40,600
you can convert all the dowry given to me
by Grand Tutor's Mansion

204
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,080
into my private assets

205
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,340
and let me manage them.

206
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,270
You're a woman.

207
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,870
Why do you want so many assets?

208
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:54,720
Precisely because I am a woman,

209
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:57,480
and my relationship with my father
is not harmonious,

210
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,750
I need some private assets to rely on.

211
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:05,120
Surely you can
meet such a simple condition, right?

212
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,670
Okay.

213
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:10,550
After we marry,

214
00:12:10,550 --> 00:12:13,870
all your dowry will belong to you.

215
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:16,510
Deal. Thank you, General.

216
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:19,320
Since we are about to marry,

217
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,030
go with me to the palace tomorrow

218
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,230
to pay respects to the empress dowager.

219
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:25,520
The empress dowager is my aunt.

220
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:28,480
And she bestowed our marriage.

221
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,790
As her juniors,

222
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,510
we should pay our respects.

223
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:34,790
Isn't that right, my future wife?

224
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,080
Okay.

225
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,240
Just wait.

226
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:43,350
Once I take back Chunliu Garden,

227
00:12:43,550 --> 00:12:45,600
I have plenty of ways to divorce you.
